So I'm withdrawing us.

756
00:42:31,908 --> 00:42:33,037
What'd he say?

757
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:36,438
He said he is resigning.

758
00:42:36,931 --> 00:42:38,388
You did not honor
your own rules.

759
00:42:47,888 --> 00:42:50,456
