764
00:43:11,478 --> 00:43:14,680
Have a drink.
It'll make me look younger.

765
00:43:14,748 --> 00:43:18,117
I'm not gonna watch you
feel sorry for yourself.

766
00:43:18,184 --> 00:43:20,152
I feel sorry for all of us.

767
00:43:20,220 --> 00:43:22,588
Don's over there
surrendering right now.

768
00:43:22,656 --> 00:43:24,557
Would you stop?

769
00:43:26,993 --> 00:43:29,728
There was a kid
on the destroyer...

770
00:43:29,796 --> 00:43:31,897
P.F.C. Brycen...

771
00:43:31,965 --> 00:43:33,966
And he was
an honest-to-goodness poet.

772
00:43:34,034 --> 00:43:35,834
- And then during...
- Roger.

773
00:43:35,902 --> 00:43:37,603
I don't want to hear it.

774
00:43:37,671 --> 00:43:40,339
My husband's gonna be
in uniform any day now.

775
00:43:40,407 --> 00:43:42,474
How do you think
he's gonna feel

776
00:43:42,542 --> 00:43:46,178
