some Pete Campbell goes
to some Vietnamese doctor?

777
00:43:48,582 --> 00:43:51,050
Since when is forgiveness
a better quality
than loyalty?

778
00:43:53,620 --> 00:43:55,454
Roger, I know it was awful

779
00:43:55,522 --> 00:43:59,491
And I know it'll never seem
like it was that long ago,

780
00:43:59,559 --> 00:44:03,062
But you fought
to make the world
a safer place and you won

781
00:44:03,129 --> 00:44:05,130
And now it is.

782
00:44:05,198 --> 00:44:06,966
You think so?

783
00:44:07,033 --> 00:44:08,500
Really?

784
00:44:08,568 --> 00:44:10,002
I have to.

785
00:44:11,838 --> 00:44:13,672
- Anything else?
- No.

786
00:44:22,349 --> 00:44:25,184
Good afternoon.
Your daughter's
psychiatrist called.

