with Mr. Saito.

790
00:44:46,339 --> 00:44:49,208
It seems Honda was never
going to leave Grey,

791
00:44:49,275 --> 00:44:52,745
But of the three princes
invited to meet the princess,

792
00:44:52,812 --> 00:44:54,546
You were the most charming.

793
00:44:54,614 --> 00:44:57,249
We're first in the door
on their little car.

794
00:44:57,317 --> 00:45:00,185
- And c.G.C.?
- Out of the running.

795
00:45:00,253 --> 00:45:01,654
We killed him.

796
00:45:03,456 --> 00:45:06,725
That stunt you pulled
was unseemly.

797
00:45:08,695 --> 00:45:10,663
- The only reason
I let you continue...
