798
00:45:12,799 --> 00:45:15,267
Do you think Joan
can rent stage space
without talking to me?

799
00:45:17,037 --> 00:45:19,104
I let you

800
00:45:19,172 --> 00:45:21,106
Because I realized
that our financial future

801
00:45:21,174 --> 00:45:23,709
